|CKBThe Charlatan Line: Confidential, Naturally|000

  charlatan <message>       Speak to the Confidence
  cchat <message>           A shorter lie for the same line
  echarlatan <emote>        Emote manually
  ecchat <emote>            The shorter manual emote
  charlatan :<soul emote>   Use a channel soul

Media links and soul emotes work as they do on the other guild lines.

  guild Charlatan muff
  guild Charlatan unmuff
  guild Charlatan color <color>

Muffling the line is called "incognito" on cwho. It sounds much better than
"ignoring everyone."
